high_descs: Move to the counter in between the two sinks.
Put the bar of soap down on the counter in between the sinks.
Walk to the gold bin in the corner of the room.
Put the bar of soap down in the bin.
Walk back over to the sink.
Pick up the bar of soap to the left of the spray bottle.
Turn and walk back to the gold bin.
Put the bar of soap in the gold bin to the left of the first bar of soap.
anns.task_desc: To move two bars of soap to the gold bin.

high_descs: Turn around and walk towards the wall, then hang a right and walk up to the counter.
Pick up the closest bar of soap off of the counter.
Turn around and walk to the door, then turn right and walk over to the golden can on the ground in the corner of the room.
Put the bar of soap into the golden can.
Turn around and take two steps, then turn left and walk up to the counter.
Pick up the bar of soap that is closest to the mirror on the counter.
Turn around and walk over to the door, then turn right and walk up to the golden can.
Put the bar of soap into the small golden can.
anns.task_desc: Move two bars of soap from the counter to a golden can.

high_descs: Turn left, go to counter between two sinks.
Pick up front soap, directly in front of candle.
Turn around, go to door.  Turn right, go to garbage can.
Place soap in garbage can.
Turn right, go to counter between two sinks.
Pick up soap from back of counter, directly left of spray bottle.
Turn around, go to door.  Turn right, go to garbage can.
Place soap in garbage can right of other soap.
anns.task_desc: Move two bars of soap from counter to garbage can.
